Project Title: Add-to-Cart Program

Description:
This project implements a simple add-to-cart functionality, allowing users to select items and add them to a virtual shopping cart.

Features:

Product Listing: Displays a list of available products with their names, descriptions, and prices.
Add to Cart: Enables users to click on a "Add to Cart" button to add selected products to their cart.
Cart Display: Shows the contents of the user's cart, including product names, quantities, and total prices.
Checkout: Provides a checkout process where users can review their order, apply any discounts or coupons, and proceed to payment.